{"tid":565640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【曬命】【遲左】我情人節收花","createTime":"2018-02-19T07:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T07:36:31.000Z","uid":39673,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa1648326077200eeb92cd300b6b93f487d9854","tid":565640,"uid":39673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:36:31.000Z","msg":"情人節我男朋友一早9點幾就出左門口，因為佢要睇花市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就留係屋企瞓教 因為我凌晨4點幾5點先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(其實時差由一開始一齊已經有，不過雙方都冇乜大問題)(至少我覺得冇)<br />\n最後我瞓到夜晚10點幾先死出門口去花市搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中間有廿幾個未接來電<br />\n好彩最後男朋友仔冇嬲我好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲送花俾我<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s9Ivs8K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs9Ivs8K.jpg&h=c2fba648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14號收既水仙現況，勁靚勁香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1oaVTJJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1oaVTJJ.jpg&h=ec9cac0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有紮銀柳，都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我地仲去左旺角標記打冷 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢竟然唔提我叫埋蠔餅</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食飯相就唔擺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 影到佢個死人樣拎住支獅威<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0GFlgqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0GFlgqC.jpg&h=0e6d8813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年初一朝早佢檔野收檔仲留多盤蘭花俾我送俾屋企人<br />\n成個情人節就係咁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有實際慶祝過之餘我又有足夠時間休息好滿足呀"}]}